      <title>一个好看的音乐播放器插件！</title>
      <link>https://cvkno80098.github.io/2023/09/07/%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%A5%BD%E7%9C%8B%E7%9A%84%E9%9F%B3%E4%B9%90%E6%92%AD%E6%94%BE%E5%99%A8%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6%EF%BC%81/</link>
      <guid>https://cvkno80098.github.io/2023/09/07/%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%A5%BD%E7%9C%8B%E7%9A%84%E9%9F%B3%E4%B9%90%E6%92%AD%E6%94%BE%E5%99%A8%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6%EF%BC%81/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Sep 2023 09:59:29 GMT</pubDate>
      
        
        
      <description>
    &lt;div id=&quot;aplayer-tEfxZPhK&quot; class=&quot;aplayer aplayer-tag-marker meting-tag-marker&quot;
         data-id=&quot;8717505505&quot; data-server=&quot;netease&quot; dat</description>
        
      
      
      
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[    <div id="aplayer-tEfxZPhK" class="aplayer aplayer-tag-marker meting-tag-marker"         data-id="8717505505" data-server="netease" data-type="playlist" data-mode="circulation" data-autoplay="false" data-mutex="false" data-listmaxheight="400px" data-preload="none" data-theme="#ad7a86" data-fixed="true" data-volume="0.5" data-listfolded="true"    ></div><h2 id="开端"><a href="#开端" class="headerlink" title="开端"></a>开端</h2><p>一次，我点开了某大佬的个人博客，注意到了左下角一个小音乐播放器，当时一直热衷于HTML和CSS的我就对它产生了很大兴趣，尝试了很多当然都以失败告终</p><p>这两天突然想到什么，按F12看了看</p><p><img src="https://img1.imgtp.com/2023/09/07/x0wJefxp.png" alt="插图嗷"></p><p><del><em>嘶….这个是aplayer？</em></del></p><hr><h2 id="进入正题"><a href="#进入正题" class="headerlink" title="进入正题"></a>进入正题</h2><p>最开始咱使用的是音乐平台的<code>生成外链播放器</code>,就比如网易生成类似于</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">iframe</span> <span class="attr">frameborder</span>=<span class="string">&quot;no&quot;</span> <span class="attr">border</span>=<span class="string">&quot;0&quot;</span> <span class="attr">marginwidth</span>=<span class="string">&quot;0&quot;</span> <span class="attr">marginheight</span>=<span class="string">&quot;0&quot;</span> <span class="attr">width</span>=<span class="string">330</span> <span class="attr">height</span>=<span class="string">86</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">&quot;//music.163.com/outchain/player?type=2&amp;id=35416430&amp;auto=0&amp;height=66&quot;</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">iframe</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>的东西<br><img src="https://img1.imgtp.com/2023/09/07/FqQmhVLU.png" alt="示例图片"><br><del>—别说，有时候其实挺美观的—</del><br>但是达不到想要的效果嗷，所以还是仅仅在Music界面使用啦</p><h2 id="hexo-tag-aplayer插件"><a href="#hexo-tag-aplayer插件" class="headerlink" title="hexo-tag-aplayer插件"></a>hexo-tag-aplayer插件</h2><p>来说说这次的主角 <code>hexo-tag-aplayer</code></p><p>安装命令：</p><figure class="highlight cmd"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install --save hexo-tag-aplayer</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>我的博客使用了<code>hexo</code>下的<code>ButterFly</code>的美化插件，看看网上说<code>hexo</code>基础目录下的<code>_config.json</code>文件会有<code>aplayer</code>的设置，结果没找到，在<code>ButterFly</code>的配置文件找到了</p><figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Inject the css and script (aplayer/meting)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">aplayerInject:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">per_page:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>于是开启</p><h2 id="常用插入格式"><a href="#常用插入格式" class="headerlink" title="常用插入格式"></a>常用插入格式</h2><h3 id="Aplayer基础"><a href="#Aplayer基础" class="headerlink" title="Aplayer基础"></a>Aplayer基础</h3><table><thead><tr><th align="center">名称</th><th align="center">默认值</th><th align="center">描述</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="center">container</td><td align="center">document.querySelector(‘.aplayer’)</td><td align="center">播放器容器元素</td></tr><tr><td align="center">fixed</td><td align="center">false</td><td align="center">开启吸底模式</td></tr><tr><td align="center">mini</td><td align="center">false</td><td align="center">开启迷你模式</td></tr><tr><td align="center">autoplay</td><td align="center">false</td><td align="center">音频自动播放</td></tr><tr><td align="center">theme</td><td align="center">‘#b7daff’</td><td align="center">主题色</td></tr><tr><td align="center">loop</td><td align="center">‘all’</td><td align="center">音频循环播放, 可选值: ‘all’, ‘one’, ‘none’</td></tr><tr><td align="center">order</td><td align="center">‘list’</td><td align="center">音频循环顺序, 可选值: ‘list’, ‘random’</td></tr><tr><td align="center">preload</td><td align="center">‘auto’</td><td align="center">预加载，可选值: ‘none’, ‘metadata’, ‘auto’</td></tr><tr><td align="center">volume</td><td align="center">0.7</td><td align="center">默认音量，请注意播放器会记忆用户设置，用户手动设置音量后默认音量即失效</td></tr><tr><td align="center">audio.name</td><td align="center">-</td><td align="center">音频名称</td></tr><tr><td align="center">audio.artist</td><td align="center">-</td><td align="center">音频艺术家</td></tr><tr><td align="center">audio.url</td><td align="center">-</td><td align="center">音频链接</td></tr><tr><td align="center">audio.cover</td><td align="center">-</td><td align="center">音频封面</td></tr><tr><td align="center">audio.lrc</td><td align="center">-</td><td align="center">详情</td></tr><tr><td align="center">audio.theme</td><td align="center">-</td><td align="center">切换到此音频时的主题色，比上面的 theme 优先级高</td></tr><tr><td align="center">audio.type</td><td align="center">‘auto’</td><td align="center">可选值: ‘auto’, ‘hls’, ‘normal’ 或其他自定义类型, 详情</td></tr><tr><td align="center">customAudioType</td><td align="center">-</td><td align="center">自定义类型，详情</td></tr><tr><td align="center">mutex</td><td align="center">true</td><td align="center">互斥，阻止多个播放器同时播放，当前播放器播放时暂停其他播放器</td></tr><tr><td align="center">lrcType</td><td align="center">0</td><td align="center">详情</td></tr><tr><td align="center">listFolded</td><td align="center">false</td><td align="center">列表默认折叠</td></tr><tr><td align="center">listMaxHeight</td><td align="center">-</td><td align="center">列表最大高度</td></tr><tr><td align="center">storageName</td><td align="center">‘aplayer-setting’</td><td align="center">存储播放器设置的 localStorage key</td></tr></tbody></table><h3 id="MeingJS"><a href="#MeingJS" class="headerlink" title="MeingJS"></a>MeingJS</h3><table><thead><tr><th align="center">选项</th><th align="center">默认值</th><th align="center">描述</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="center">id</td><td align="center">必须值</td><td align="center">歌曲 id &#x2F; 播放列表 id &#x2F; 相册 id &#x2F; 搜索关键字</td></tr><tr><td align="center">server</td><td align="center">必须值</td><td align="center">音乐平台: netease, tencent, kugou, xiami, baidu</td></tr><tr><td align="center">type</td><td align="center">必须值</td><td align="center">song, playlist, album, search, artist</td></tr><tr><td align="center">fixed</td><td align="center">false</td><td align="center">开启固定模式</td></tr><tr><td align="center">mini</td><td align="center">false</td><td align="center">开启迷你模式</td></tr><tr><td align="center">loop</td><td align="center">all</td><td align="center">列表循环模式：all, one,none</td></tr><tr><td align="center">order</td><td align="center">list</td><td align="center">列表播放模式： list, random</td></tr><tr><td align="center">volume</td><td align="center">0.7</td><td align="center">播放器音量</td></tr><tr><td align="center">lrctype</td><td align="center">0</td><td align="center">歌词格式类型</td></tr><tr><td align="center">listfolded</td><td align="center">false</td><td align="center">指定音乐播放列表是否折叠</td></tr><tr><td align="center">storagename</td><td align="center">metingjs</td><td align="center">LocalStorage 中存储播放器设定的键名</td></tr><tr><td align="center">autoplay</td><td align="center">true</td><td align="center">自动播放，移动端浏览器暂时不支持此功能</td></tr><tr><td align="center">mutex</td><td align="center">true</td><td align="center">该选项开启时，如果同页面有其他 aplayer 播放，该播放器会暂停</td></tr><tr><td align="center">listmaxheight</td><td align="center">340px</td><td align="center">播放列表的最大长度</td></tr><tr><td align="center">preload</td><td align="center">auto</td><td align="center">音乐文件预载入模式，可选项： none, metadata, auto</td></tr><tr><td align="center">theme</td><td align="center">#ad7a86</td><td align="center">播放器风格色彩设置</td></tr></tbody></table><h2 id="示例【MeingJS】"><a href="#示例【MeingJS】" class="headerlink" title="示例【MeingJS】"></a>示例【MeingJS】</h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% meting &quot;8717505505&quot; &quot;netease&quot; &quot;playlist&quot; &quot;fixed&quot; &quot;mutex:false&quot; &quot;listmaxheight:400px&quot; &quot;volume:0.5&quot; &quot;preload:none&quot; &quot;listfolded&quot; &quot;theme:#ad7a86&quot;%&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>您可以将其任意插入在文档中<br><em>注意，这里使用了<code>MetingJS</code>。请检查您是否开启</em></p><h2 id="结尾：各个项目坐标及解释"><a href="#结尾：各个项目坐标及解释" class="headerlink" title="结尾：各个项目坐标及解释"></a>结尾：各个项目坐标及解释</h2><p><a href="https://github.com/DIYgod/APlayer"><code>aplayer</code>: 🍭 Wow, such a beautiful HTML5 music player</a></p><ul><li>中文Docs：<a href="https://aplayer.js.org/#/zh-Hans">https://aplayer.js.org/#/zh-Hans</a></li></ul><p>插件列表</p><blockquote><p>[hexo] hexo-tag-aplayer: <a href="https://github.com/MoePlayer/hexo-tag-aplayer">https://github.com/MoePlayer/hexo-tag-aplayer</a><br>[Typecho] APlayer-Typecho-Plugin: <a href="https://github.com/zgq354/APlayer-Typecho-Plugin">https://github.com/zgq354/APlayer-Typecho-Plugin</a><br>[WordPress] Hermit-X(APlayer for WordPress): <a href="https://github.com/liwanglin12/Hermit-X">https://github.com/liwanglin12/Hermit-X</a><br>[Z-BlogPHP] APlayer_for_Z-BlogPHP: <a href="https://github.com/fghrsh/APlayer_for_Z-BlogPHP">https://github.com/fghrsh/APlayer_for_Z-BlogPHP</a><br>[React] react-aplayer: <a href="https://github.com/sabrinaluo/react-aplayer">https://github.com/sabrinaluo/react-aplayer</a><br>[Vue] Vue-APlayer: <a href="https://github.com/SevenOutman/vue-aplayer">https://github.com/SevenOutman/vue-aplayer</a><br>[Vue] vue-aplayer: <a href="https://github.com/MoeFE/vue-aplayer">https://github.com/MoeFE/vue-aplayer</a><br>[PHP] php-aplayer: <a href="https://github.com/Daryl-L/php-aplayer">https://github.com/Daryl-L/php-aplayer</a><br>[Hugo] aplayer-hugo-module: <a href="https://github.com/Runzelee/aplayer-hugo-module">https://github.com/Runzelee/aplayer-hugo-module</a>  </p></blockquote><p><a href="https://github.com/metowolf/MetingJS"><code>MetingJS</code>: work with Meting music API</a></p>]]></content:encoded>
      
      
